Apply.Name: Apply 1
Apply.SQLExpression: "N$10204" as (SELECT PREDICTION("SVM" USING *) "SVM_PRED", PREDICTION("SVM_GAUSSIAN" USING *) "SVM_GAUSSIAN_PRED", PREDICTION("SVM_LINEAR" USING *) "SVM_LINEAR_PRED", PREDICTION("SVM_ACTIVE" USING *) "SVM_ACTIVE_PRED", PREDICTION("SVM_GAUSSIAN_ACTIVE" USING *) "SVM_GAUSSIAN_ACTIVE_PRED", PREDICTION("SVM_LINEAR_ACTIVE" USING *) "SVM_LINEAR_ACTIVE_PRED", "URL" FROM {INPUT_SOURCE} )

Apply.Name: Apply 2
Apply.SQLExpression: "N$10208" as (SELECT PREDICTION("GLM_RIGED" USING *) "GLM_RIGED_PRED", PREDICTION_BOUNDS("GLM_RIGED", 0.95 USING *).LOWER "GLM_RIGED_PBLW", PREDICTION_BOUNDS("GLM_RIGED", 0.95 USING *).UPPER "GLM_RIGED_PBUP", PREDICTION("GLM_SELECTION0" USING *) "GLM_SELECTION0_PRED", PREDICTION_BOUNDS("GLM_SELECTION0", 0.95 USING *).LOWER "GLM_SELECTION0_PBLW", PREDICTION_BOUNDS("GLM_SELECTION0", 0.95 USING *).UPPER "GLM_SELECTION0_PBUP", PREDICTION("GLM_GENERATION" USING *) "GLM_GENERATION_PRED", PREDICTION_BOUNDS("GLM_GENERATION", 0.95 USING *).LOWER "GLM_GENERATION_PBLW", PREDICTION_BOUNDS("GLM_GENERATION", 0.95 USING *).UPPER "GLM_GENERATION_PBUP", "URL", "SHARES" FROM {INPUT_SOURCE} )
